624
00:31:08,490 --> 00:31:09,730
Young Master.

625
00:31:09,860 --> 00:31:11,220
Greetings.

626
00:31:11,380 --> 00:31:13,680
Isn't this the eldest daughter of Duke Lu,

627
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:15,680
