628
00:31:15,930 --> 00:31:16,440
What...

629
00:31:16,920 --> 00:31:19,600
What are you doing?

630
00:31:20,050 --> 00:31:20,900
Young Master,

631
00:31:21,460 --> 00:31:22,560
I have something

632
00:31:22,710 --> 00:31:24,550
